headline: Crowdstrike Holdings Inc. (CRWD) Rated as a ‘Buy’ at Truist Securities
summary: Crowdstrike Holdings Inc. (NASDAQ:CRWD) is one of the best tech stocks to buy for the long term. On September 8, Truist Securities reiterated a ‘Buy’ rating on the stock and a $500 price target. The positive stance follows the stock’s impressive run, marked by a 71% gain over the past year.
